Pergunta: "What is the number of the highest-value bidding process in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT NUMERO_LICITACAO FROM LICITACAO WHERE VALOR_ESTIMADO = (SELECT MAX(VALOR_ESTIMADO) FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024) AND ANO_LICITACAO = 2024;

Pergunta: "What is the value of the highest-value bidding process in 2023?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT MAX(VALOR_ESTIMADO) AS MAIOR_VALOR FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2023;

Pergunta: "Which organizations are responsible for the bidding processes registered in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT DISTINCT ORGAO FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024;

Pergunta: "How many bidding processes were registered in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024

Pergunta: "What are the numbers of the bidding processes opened in January 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT NUMERO_LICITACAO FROM dbo.LICITACAO WHERE DATEPART(year, DATA_ABERTURA) = 2024 AND DATEPART(month, DATA_ABERTURA) = 1;

Pergunta: "What was the status of the bidding process with the highest adjudicated value in 2023?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT STATUS_ANALISE FROM LICITACAO WHERE VALOR_ADJUDICADO = (SELECT MAX(VALOR_ADJUDICADO) FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2023) AND ANO_LICITACAO = 2023

Pergunta: "How many bidding processes opened in 2024 have an estimated value above 1 million reais?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT COUNT(ID_ENTIDADE) AS ContagemProcessos FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024 AND VALOR_ESTIMADO > 1000000.000;

Pergunta: "Which bidding processes have the adjudication type as 'Lowest Price'?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT * FROM LICITACAO WHERE TIPO_ADJUDICACAO = 'Menor Preço'

Pergunta: "What were the 5 bidding processes with the highest adjudicated values in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT TOP 5 NUMERO_LICITACAO, VALOR_ADJUDICADO, ANO_LICITACAO FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024 ORDER BY VALOR_ADJUDICADO DESC;

Pergunta: "What is the average estimated value of the bidding processes registered in 2023?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT AVG(VALOR_ESTIMADO) AS [Média do Valor Estimado] FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2023;

Pergunta: "Which organization conducted the most bidding processes in 2022?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT TOP 1 ORGAO, COUNT(NUMERO_LICITACAO) AS TOTAL_LICITACOES FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2022 GROUP BY ORGAO ORDER BY TOTAL_LICITACOES DESC;

Pergunta: "How many bidding processes were conducted by each entity in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT ID_ENTIDADE, COUNT(NUMERO_LICITACAO) AS QUANTIDADE_PROCESSOS FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024 GROUP BY ID_ENTIDADE;

Pergunta: "How many bidding processes have the legislation specified as 'Law 14333'?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM LICON_DEV.dbo.LICITACAO AS L INNER JOIN LICON_DEV.dbo.LEGISLACAO AS LG ON L.ID_LEGISLACAO = LG.ID_LEGISLACAO WHERE LG.NOME_LEGISLACAO = 'Law 14333';

Pergunta: "For each organization
Consulta_SQL: SELECT ORGAO, SUM(VALOR_ESTIMADO) AS VALOR_ESTIMADO_TOTAL FROM LICITACAO GROUP BY ORGAO;

Pergunta: "Which bidding processes have an estimated value above 500 thousand reais and are still under review?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT * FROM LICON_DEV.dbo.LICITACAO WHERE VALOR_ESTIMADO > 500000 AND STATUS_ANALISE = 'EM ANÁLISE'

Pergunta: "How many bidding processes had exclusive participation in 2024?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT COUNT(*) FROM ( SELECT ID_ENTIDADE_PARTICIPANTE FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = 2024 GROUP BY ID_ENTIDADE_PARTICIPANTE HAVING COUNT(ID_ENTIDADE_PARTICIPANTE) = 1 ) AS Subquery;

Pergunta: "Which were the top 3 organizations that conducted the most bidding processes in the last 5 years
Consulta_SQL: SELECT TOP 3 ORGAO, COUNT(*) AS QUANTIDADE FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO >= YEAR(GETDATE()) - 5 GROUP BY ORGAO ORDER BY QUANTIDADE DESC;

Pergunta: "Who are the top 5 users who registered the most bidding processes in the last 12 months
Consulta_SQL: SELECT TOP 5 ID_USUARIO, COUNT(ID_USUARIO) AS TOTAL_PROCESSOS FROM LICITACAO WHERE DATA_CADASTRO_PUBLICACAO >= DATEADD(year, -1, GETDATE()) GROUP BY ID_USUARIO ORDER BY TOTAL_PROCESSOS DESC;

Pergunta: "For each participating entity
Consulta_SQL: SELECT ID_ENTIDADE_PARTICIPANTE, COUNT(*) AS CONT_LICITACOES FROM dbo.LICITACAO GROUP BY ID_ENTIDADE_PARTICIPANTE

Pergunta: "Which bidding processes had estimated values higher than the average of all bidding processes in the same year?"
Consulta_SQL: SELECT NUMERO_LICITACAO, VALOR_ESTIMADO, ANO_LICITACAO FROM LICITACAO WHERE VALOR_ESTIMADO > ( SELECT AVG(VALOR_ESTIMADO) FROM LICITACAO WHERE ANO_LICITACAO = ANO_LICITACAO );
